                             White Paper 
                          
                          Penetration Testing helps organizations meet compliance requirements and uncover security risks. 
                        


                      While the adage "the best offense is a good defense" may be well worn, it is still true - especially for your network's security. A great proactive approach to managing your company's network security can be penetration testing. A penetration test can help show how an attacker would gain unauthorized access to your environment through your email systems, firewalls, VPN tunnels, web servers and other network devices.
                  
SecureWorks can help you find security risks through testing and assessment services.
For over a decade, SecureWorks has provided a comprehensive suite of IT security services to thousands of clients. Fueled by Counter Threat Unit (CTU) intelligence, we can help you anticipate your cyber attackers, detect their tradecraft, disrupt the kill chain and eradicate their presence in your environment.
