									  Company					  

  

Company
CLOUD SECURITY CORPORATION is a leading technology company focused on the next generation of Internet and mobile security. We offer a suite of comprehensive solutions that includes Cloud Security, Application Security and Mobile Security (Bring-Your-Own-Device  –  BYOD).CLOUD SECURITY is an emerging brand, though already recognized in the cloud computing industry.  Rather than compete with large players on usage and connectivity, our vision is to develop security solutions to a changing world.
At CLOUD SECURITY, we are committed to research and development, and are striving to create a safe and secure future for all computing environments and technologies.  Specifically, our goal is to protect and control clients’ confidential information with our patent-pending encryption methodologies that keep data private and help meet regulatory compliance requirements.
 
 
 

