For Infrastructure & Operations Professionals
The Forrester Wave™: Private Cloud Software Suites, Q1 2016
How The Top Nine Private Cloud Software Suites Stack Up
January 19, 2016
					







Authors

By 
										Lauren E. Nelson

with 
										Glenn O'Donnell, 
							

Dave Bartoletti, 
							
Michael Caputo
							










Why Read This Report
In Forrester's 40-criteria evaluation of private cloud solution vendors, we identified the nine most significant software providers — BMC Software, Cisco Systems, Citrix, Hewlett Packard Enterprise, Huawei, IBM, Microsoft, Red Hat, and VMware — in the category and researched, analyzed, and scored them. This report details our findings to help infrastructure and operations (I&O) professionals select the optimum private cloud solution. I&O pros can customize criteria weightings to align with their own private cloud initiative. It is a refresh to Forrester's "The Forrester Wave™: Private Cloud Solutions, Q4 2013" report. 




Tags

Cloud Computing, 
Private Cloud




