451 Research: How to Create a Quick Comparative Multi-Cloud TCO Analysis Spanning Public, Private and Managed Cloud Analyst


Analyst Report
                
                


PDF
578 kb


13 pages






Overview

Comparing the cost of private, public and managed cloud can be complex, often taking days or weeks to complete. This 451 research report, commissioned by Hewlett Packard Enterprise, provides a simple way to do a price comparison in mere minutes. Ideal for enterprises that don’t have time to do a full TCO analysis, you can use this report to quickly determine how the cost of ...
Comparing the cost of private, public and managed cloud can be complex, often taking days or weeks to complete. This 451 research report, commissioned by Hewlett Packard Enterprise, provides a simple way to do a price comparison in mere minutes. Ideal for enterprises that don’t have time to do a full TCO analysis, you can use this report to quickly determine how the cost of your private cloud compares to the cost of public clouds.


